## {{#if (eq project.language "pt-BR")}}Escopo de Negocio (Regra #5){{else}}Business Scope (Rule #5){{/if}}

{{#if (eq project.language "pt-BR")}}
**PERMITIDO**: regras deterministicas (engine sem LLM), pipelines de processamento, integracao com LLMs, schedulers e jobs, alertas e notificacoes.

**PROIBIDO**: logica de API/frontend, extracao de dados de sistemas externos (modulo dedicado), auditoria (modulo dedicado).
{{else}}
**ALLOWED**: deterministic rules (engine without LLM), processing pipelines, LLM integration, schedulers and jobs, alerts and notifications.

**FORBIDDEN**: API/frontend logic, external data extraction (dedicated module), auditing (dedicated module).
{{/if}}

